	* vfile/vhttp/Attic/http.h, vfile/vhttp/Attic/req.txt, vfile/vhttp/Attic/test_vhttp.c, vfile/vhttp/Attic/vhttp.c, vfile/vhttp/Attic/vhttp.h, vfile/vftp/Attic/.cvsignore, vfile/vftp/Attic/ftp.c, vfile/vftp/Attic/ftp.h, vfile/vftp/Attic/test_vftp.c, vfile/vftp/Attic/vftp.c, vfile/vftp/Attic/vftp.h, vfile/vhttp/Attic/.cvsignore, vfile/vhttp/Attic/Makefile.am, vfile/vhttp/Attic/base64.c, vfile/vhttp/Attic/http.c, vfile/vfff/.cvsignore, vfile/vfff/Attic/ftp.h, vfile/vfff/Attic/http.h, vfile/vfff/Makefile.am, vfile/vfff/base64.c, vfile/vfff/ftp.c, vfile/vfff/http.c, vfile/vfff/vfff.c, vfile/vfff/vfff.h, vfile/Attic/vfvftp.c, vfile/Attic/vfvhttp.c, vfile/vfprogress.c, vfile/vfreq.c, vfile/vfreq.h, vfile/.cvsignore, vfile/Attic/uncompr.c, vfile/Makefile.am, vfile/fetch.c, vfile/misc.c, vfile/test_retr.sh, vfile/vfetch.c, vfile/vfffmod.c, vfile/vfget.c, vfile/vfile.c, vfile/vfile.h:
	- vftp and vhttp merge into vfff sublib (VFile's File Fetch)
	- file aren't downloaded if local copy has the same mtime and size
	- general code cleanups

2003-01-23  Tomasz Pala  <gotar@pld.org.pl>

	* doc/pl/poldek.pod: - typos reported by bufi <bufi@solar.fn.pl>

2003-01-21  Pawe³ Gajda  <mis@pld.org.pl>

	* conf.c: - file inclusion improvements:
	   - non-absolute paths are prefixed by parent file's dirname
	   - included file could be remote one, i.e declaration below now works:
	       %include http://foo/poldek.conf

	- '_' prefixed parameters are treated as user-level, private variables, e.g.
	   configuration below now works:

	   _pld_ra_rootdir = ftp://ftp.pld.org.pl/dists/ra
	   source = ra  %{_pld_ra_rootdir}/PLD/i686/PLD/RPMS/
	   source = ra-updates-security %{_pld_ra_rootdir}/updates/security/i686/

	* Attic/main.c: - die on configuration loading failure

2003-01-21  Tomasz K³oczko  <kloczek@pld.org.pl>

	* vfjuggle: - change default VF_MNTPOINT to /mnt/cdrom.

2003-01-21  Pawe³ Gajda  <mis@pld.org.pl>

	* sigint/Makefile.am, Attic/lib_install.c, Attic/main.c, conf.c, lib_init.c, make.sh, misc.c, pkgset-install.c, pkgset.c, pkgset.h, poldek.h:
	- minor changes

	* pkg.c, pkg.h:
	- "arch" and "os" moved to global dictionary (saves about 10 bytes memory
	   per packege)
	- added NVR member and coresponding cmp* functions;
	  simplifies "poldek --shell"-like apps

	* Attic/poldek.alias: - removed fun alias

	* pkgdir/pkg_restore.c, pkgdir/pkg_store.c, pkgdir/pkgdir.h, pkgdir/pndir/save.c:
	- PKGSTORE_DEFAULT_* macros changed to public const char[]s

	* shell/Attic/search.c: - matching shell patterns case insensitive
	- paths matching bugfix (#511)
	- bugfix: search -ld was extremely slow because of wrong order
	  of description and file list retrieval from package index.

	* shell/Attic/desc.c: - disabled testing stuff

