	- /bin/rpm is executed on pty (via p_ty_open())
	- fixed --log opt
	- shell: file transfer could by C-c'ed
	- fixed pkgdir's open_idx*() functions
	- i18n work
	- doc's updates

	* vfile/Attic/vfcurl.h, vfile/Attic/vfvftp.c, vfile/Makefile.am, vfile/fetch.c, vfile/p_open.c, vfile/vfcurl.c, vfile/vfile.c, vfile/vfile.h, vfile/vfprogress.c:
	- vfcurl: transfer is able to be interrupted by SIGINT
	- added vfvftp module
	- removed rpmio (it's useless)
	- added vfprogress
	- few code improvements

	* vfile/vftp/Attic/Makefile.am, vfile/vftp/Attic/ftp.c, vfile/vftp/Attic/ftp.h, vfile/vftp/Attic/test_vftp.c, vfile/vftp/Attic/vftp.c, vfile/vftp/Attic/vftp.h, vfile/vftp/Attic/.cvsignore:
	- simple FTP retriever

